summary:
Meeting Of The Minds 

Thrax: "Do you two know who the heck that robot guy is?" Pitch: "No." Loki: "I haven't seen that machine...
caption:
Meeting Of The Minds

Thrax: “Do you two know who the heck that robot guy is?”

Pitch: “No.”

Loki: “I haven’t seen that machine until now.”

Thrax: “But you’re from the same universe as him!”

Loki: “Just because we’re from the same universe doesn’t mean I know everyone from there!”

I would love to have Ultron and Nefarious to meet up to have conversations with each other! It would be such a cool talk!
